{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event07","nameNarration":"Kuroe","narration":"The rise in scams and theft in Takarazaki@has been linked to a criminal organization...@Well, according to the news, anyway.","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"On the off chance that a Witch@really is responsible for this,@how am I supposed to find it@if it's been flying under the radar?"},{"narration":"For now, I think I'm going to go poke@around areas that seem unsafe."},{"narration":"Instead of searching for traces of a Witch's magic,@I could keep an eye out for the crimes themselves.@That might not be a bad idea, actually."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21573.jpg","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21133.jpg","turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21603.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"...Figured as much.","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"This sort of thing is impossible enough as it is,@huh..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I've been scouring all sorts of places for the past@three days...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...but I still haven't found any Witches,@no matter how hard I look.)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Incidents kept cropping up in the area...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...and even if they weren't caused by a Witch...)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...how could I not have seen a single one@of them...?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Thinking about it more...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...what's the worst thing I could possibly happen@to pass by? A mugging?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Trying to keep an eye out for signs of crime,@rather than signs of a Witch...)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Actually, wait, how can I even tell if someone's@likely to commit a crime...?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":1}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"[flashEffect:flashRed1][chara:104301:effect_shake]...Ugh..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Again, huh...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Lately, even after I purify my Soul Gem,@it immediately starts getting cloudy again.)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I'm conserving my magic power and everything,@too...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"I wonder why...Tamaki-san...?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bg":"bg_adv_20312.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":800402,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104300,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_window.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.5,"turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime04","chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"My father and I didn't see each other very often...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"ef_adv_10"},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...so I'm a little nervous about meeting him again."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I'm worried that he'll be disappointed..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...to find out that I'm still a complete nobody."},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"He won't be."},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"I bet he'll be happy just to see you."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Yeah..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I'm sure he'll be delighted with just that..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402},{"id":104300,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"And yet..."},{"chara":[{"id":800402}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"As the one who got left behind, I still can't@forgive myself..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bgm":"stop","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21723.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.5,"turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","surround":"7009_night_townbuzz","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.2},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(The next place I want to go to is two stops@away...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(The train's still running, right...?)"},{"au