)"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(On top of not getting anything done, the Witch@completely ignored me...)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...I can't just stand around doing nothing.)"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I should chase after it...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Which reminds me, that metallic smell...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"...Hm?"},{"chara":[{"id":104300}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"It's gone too...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I swear it wasn't my imagination...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(What if there are people under the control@of a Witch's Kiss out there somewhere...?)"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I-I don't know, though...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(The guy who ran past me earlier might've been@injured...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(But I don't know where he went, either,@or if he even left the station.)"},{"chara":[{"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I can't smell anything anymore...)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(What do I do? Where do I start?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(W-well, first, I have 